  author    = "Dangarikar, Chaitali and
               Bhattacharya, Arnab and
               N J, Karthika and
               Terdalkar, Hrishikesh and
               Bhattacharyya, Pramit and
               Kulkarni, Annarao and
               Lakkundi, Chaitanya S and
