  code   = "https://github.com/hrishikeshrt/vaiyyakarana",
  abstract = "\\textit{Vaiyyākaraṇaḥ} is a Telegram bot aimed towards helping the learners of Sanskrit grammar (vyākaraṇa). The salient features of \\textit{Vaiyyākaraṇaḥ} are: stem finder (prātipadikam), declension generation (subantāḥ), root finder (dhātuḥ), conjugation generation (tiṅantāḥ) and word segmentation (sandhisamāsau). State-of-the-art datasets, tools and technologies are used to offer these capabilities.",
